                         <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5814GHII">Apocryphal Acts of the Apostles (Recension II)</title>

                         <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                         <hi rend="rubric">በስመ: አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመን</hi>ፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አሐዱ፡ አምላክ፡
                         <hi rend="rubric">ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ግብ</hi>ሮሙ፡ ለሐዋርያት፡
                         ወባዕ<hi rend="rubric">ዳንሂ፡ እምሰብዓ፡ ወክልኤቱ፡ አርድእት።</hi> ወዘኮነ፡ ኵሉ፡
                         እምኔሆሙ፡<hi rend="rubric"> ወለእለ፡ አዕረፉ፡ ጸሎቶሙ፡</hi> ወበረከቶሙ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="DN"/>
                         ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘአስተጋብኡ፡ ቦቱ፡ ግብረ፡ አርድእት፡ ኅሩያን፡ አርድእቱ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ <hi rend="rubric">ኢየሱስ፡</hi> ክርስቶስ፡ ወመድኃኒነ፨
                         ቃሉ፡ ለ<hi rend="rubric">እግዚአብሔር፡</hi> ሕያው፡ ወዘ፲ወ፪ሐዋርያት፡ ንጹሐን፡ ወቅዱሳን፡ ወቡሩካን፡
                      </incipit>
                         <note>The collection contained in the manuscript belongs to Recension II (see <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/PMRJZ4A4"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Bausi2000Osservazioni"/><title level="a">Alcune osservazioni sul Gadla ḥawāryāt</title><title level="j">Annali dell’Istituto Orientale di Napoli</title><author><forename>Alessandro</forename><surname>Bausi</surname></author><date>2000</date><biblScope unit="volume">60-61</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">77-114</biblScope><note type="url">https://www.academia.edu/1151410/Alcune_osservazioni_sul_Gadla_%E1%B8%A5aw%C4%81ry%C4%81t</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Bausi2000Osservazioni</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Bausi2000Osservazioni</note><citedRange unit="page">83</citedRange></bibl>).
